No. 09-1567. James D. Lee, Petitioner v. Astoria Generating Company, L.P., et al. 562 U.S. 948, 131 S. Ct. 215,

178 L. Ed. 2d 244,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 7847. October 4, 2010.

Motion of Maritime Law Association of the United States for leave to file a brief as amicus curiae granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the Court of Appeals of New York denied.

Same case below, 13 N.Y.3d 382, 892 N.Y.S.2d 294, 920 N.E.2d 350.
